## Important Files

| File | Purpose |
|------|---------|
| `app/page.tsx` | Main page; imports and renders all sections |
| `app/layout.tsx` | Root layout, fonts, metadata |
| `app/globals.css` | Tailwind, AOS, Swiper, custom variables |
| `types/index.ts` | Shared types (Project, Testimonial, GalleryImage) |
| `next.config.ts` | Next.js config (images, etc.) |
| `package.json` | Dependencies, scripts (dev, build, start, lint) |

